	* doc/README.macros (USE_GET_STACKBASE_FOR_MAIN): Document.
	* os_dep.c (GC_get_main_stack_base): Recognize
	USE_GET_STACKBASE_FOR_MAIN (only if THREADS and LINUX_STACKBOTTOM)
	and use GC_get_stack_base() in this case.

