	GC_make_closure, GC_debug_invoke_finalizer,
	GC_page_was_ever_dirty, GC_is_fresh (in GC_noop).
	* thread_local_alloc.c: Don't include "gc_inline.h".
	* win32_threads.c (GC_write_fault_handler): Declare only if
	MPROTECT_VDB.

